  "original_title": "\u0dbd\u0dcf\u0dc6\u0dca \u0d9c\u0dd1\u0dc3\u0dca \u0dad\u0dc0 \u0d85\u0da9\u0dd4 \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Laughing gas will decrease further",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. W.KH Vagapitiya, Chairman of Laughs Group, says that the price of Laugh Gas will be further reduced next month.",
        "He mentioned that the price of Laf gas was reduced by 1050 rupees last week, and it will be reduced by a similar amount next month as well.",
        "The current price of a 12.5 kg cylinder of Laugh Gas is 5,800 rupees, and the price of a 5 kg cylinder is 2,320 rupees. The price of a 2.5 kg gas cylinder is 928 rupees."
      ],
